data.eml:eml: Osteology and relationships of Libanopycnodus wenzi gen. et sp. nov. and Sigmapycnodus giganteus gen. et sp. nov. (Pycnodontiformes) from the Late Cretaceous of Lebanon

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Taverne, Louis, Capasso, Luigi (2018): Osteology and relationships of Libanopycnodus wenzi gen. et sp. nov. and Sigmapycnodus giganteus gen. et sp. nov. (Pycnodontiformes) from the Late Cretaceous of Lebanon. European Journal of Taxonomy 420: 1-29, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2018.420
